name: Experiment Or Die #28
description: Day 28 of daily collages that will go for a full year using my years of photos and personal assets. Since I've been working on this collection every day I started to notice that if I took new photos and included them in my design that a time capsule of that day was created. Years from today I could look back at this design and recollect exactly what I did on October 24, 2021. And I hope something about this collection connects with you in a similar way. IG: Nikejerk
